{#-
  V3 — hybrid: V2.5's JSON-format coaching at last user turn PLUS V2's terse
  `name(params): description` per-tool rendering. Gives the LoRA both the
  "emit JSON" trigger AND the arg names + tool descriptions it was trained
  to see. Ollama's full-schema TEMPLATE is ~2400 tokens; V3 targets ~600.

  Expected fix for V2.5's 29/38 regression: missing descriptions caused
  over-firing on figurative prompts ("Schedule conflicts are the worst"),
  and missing arg names caused `convert` to emit {from, to, amount}
  instead of {value, from_unit, to_unit}.

  Assistant tool_calls rendering identical to V1/V2/V2.5.
-#}
{%- if messages -%}
{%- set has_system = (messages[0].role == 'system') -%}
{%- if has_system or tools -%}
<|start_header_id|>system<|end_header_id|>
{%- if has_system %}

{{ messages[0].content }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if tools %}

You are a helpful assistant with tool calling capabilities. When you receive a tool call response, use the output to format an answer to the orginal use question.
{%- endif %}<|eot_id|>
{%- endif -%}
{%- set dialog = messages[1:] if has_system else messages -%}
{%- for message in dialog -%}
{%- if message.role == 'user' -%}
<|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>
{%- if tools and loop.last %}

Given the following tools, please respond with a JSON for a function call with its proper arguments that best answers the given prompt. Respond in the format {"name": function name, "parameters": dictionary of argument name and its value}. Do not use variables.

Tools:
{% for t in tools -%}
{%- set fn = t.function if t.function is defined else t -%}
- {{ fn.name }}({% if fn.parameters and fn.parameters.properties %}{{ fn.parameters.properties.keys() | join(', ') }}{% endif %}): {{ fn.description | default('', true) }}
{% endfor -%}
{%- endif %}

{{ message.content }}<|eot_id|>{% if loop.last %}<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

{% endif -%}
{%- elif message.role == 'assistant' -%}
<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>
{%- if message.tool_calls %}

{% for tc in message.tool_calls -%}
{"name": "{{ tc.function.name }}", "parameters": {{ tc.function.arguments | tojson if tc.function.arguments is mapping else tc.function.arguments }}}
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}

{{ message.content }}{% if not loop.last %}<|eot_id|>{% endif %}
{%- endif -%}
{%- elif message.role == 'tool' -%}
<|start_header_id|>ipython<|end_header_id|>

{{ message.content }}<|eot_id|>{% if loop.last %}<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

{% endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- else -%}
{%- if system %}<|start_header_id|>system<|end_header_id|>

{{ system }}<|eot_id|>{% endif %}{% if prompt %}<|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>

{{ prompt }}<|eot_id|>{% endif %}<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

{% endif -%}
